dct_description_sm: Map 1 (current as of 1940 publication) has key showing "20 mile coast defense gun radius" and "Finnish territory ceded to U.S.S.R.," with various strategic notes, railroad lines, and cities. Maps 2-5 show Finlands boundaries at earlier points in history.
"For report documenting above map see Life March 25, 1940 issue pages 30-32."
